item.title: CVE-2021-34389|2024-08-04T00:12:50.025Z -- nvidia -- nvidia%20jetson%2C%20tx2%20series%2C%20tx2%20nx%2C%20agx%20xavier%20series%2C%20xavier%20nx
item.description: Trusty contains a vulnerability in NVIDIA OTE protocol message parsing code, which is present in all the TAs. An incorrect bounds check can allow a local user through a malicious client to access memory from the heap in the TrustZone, which may lead to information disclosure.
